snippet.textDisplay: Achint has been giving really good tunes back to back in the recent years (don't know much about his older music). Scam 1992, Monica O my Darling, Rocket boys and now this. Really proud of the new generation of Gujarati composers doing well at the national level. Great work by Aditya and Coke studio as well! I hope Coke studio continues giving us some really good songs and spread our culture internationally! Coke studio, "tame goti lo, goti lo" such new artists from all over India and keep making such awesome songs!
snippet.textOriginal: Achint has been giving really good tunes back to back in the recent years (don't know much about his older music). Scam 1992, Monica O my Darling, Rocket boys and now this. Really proud of the new generation of Gujarati composers doing well at the national level. Great work by Aditya and Coke studio as well! I hope Coke studio continues giving us some really good songs and spread our culture internationally! Coke studio, "tame goti lo, goti lo" such new artists from all over India and keep making such awesome songs!

We underestimate our Indian languages & ofcourse run after english just the way I'm still doing right now. But it's only music which can bind us together. Hats off to Coke studio Bharat for giving the chance to pep like me to enjoy songs in different  languages & get a different feel. The main thing I forgot to mention is the Artists❤ woh did an excellent work by adding life to song. Keep it up...
